OL,4,Con first anniversary of her death
OL,6,FA memorial service has been held in
OL,7,Fmemory of a 15-year-old girl who was
OL,8,Fstabbed to death a year ago.
OL,10,FHolly Newton, of Haltwhistle, died in
OL,11,Fhospital after suffering knife
OL,12,Finjuries in an incident in the
OL,13,FPriestpopple area of Hexham on 27
OL,14,FJanuary 2023.
OL,16,FA 16-year-old boy was also taken to
OL,17,Fhospital and suffered non-life-
OL,18,Fthreatening knife injuries in the
OL,19,Fattack after the pair made their way
OL,20,Fhome from school.
