OL,3,CMemorial service held to remember teen
OL,4,Con first anniversary of her death
OL,6,FFamily, friends and members of the
OL,7,Fpublic descended on Hexham Abbey, its
OL,8,Fancient interior lit in purple -
OL,9,FHolly's favourite colour.JFollowing
OL,10,Fthe service, flowers were laid and
OL,11,Fcandles were lit alongside messages
OL,12,Ffor the teenager and her family.
OL,14,FThe service was led by Rev Dr Henry
OL,15,FHope, who told ITV Tyne Tees: "We're
OL,16,Fgathering together in the abbey to
OL,17,Fremember Holly but also to comfort one
OL,18,Fanother and support one another as we
OL,19,Fmark this sad milestone.
