OL,3,CMemorial service held to remember teen
OL,4,Con first anniversary of her death
OL,6,F"It's important to mark it together as
OL,7,Fa community, yes of course, it's an
OL,8,Fevent that's particularly painful and
OL,9,Fmost painful of course for the family
OL,10,Fand Holly's closest friends, but it
OL,11,Fwas an event that really touched the
OL,12,Fwhole town last year.
OL,14,F"It's a sign (the service) to the
OL,15,Ffamily that they're not the only ones
OL,16,Fwho will be remembering Holly, that
OL,17,Fthey don't stand alone in their grief
OL,18,Fbut that they are supported by the
OL,19,Fwhole community."
