OL,3,CMemorial service held to remember teen
OL,4,Con first anniversary of her death
OL,6,FAhead of the anniversary, Holly's
OL,7,Fmother Micala Trussler, said:
OL,8,F"Everyone is welcome to join our
OL,9,Ffamily and friends of Holly Newton in
OL,10,Fan act of remembrance at Hexham Abbey.
OL,12,F"A moment of silent reflection will be
OL,13,Ffollowed by some words from Curate
OL,14,FHenry Hope and tributes from myself
OL,15,Fand friends. Attendees are welcome to
OL,16,Flight a candle and there will be the
OL,17,Fopportunity to dedicate special purple
OL,18,Fstars in Holly's memory as part of the
OL,19,FAbbey's Stars for Eternity
OL,20,Finstallation."
