OL,6,F"For those unable to attend, stars can
OL,7,Fbe dedicated in the Abbey between now
OL,8,Fand Tuesday 30 January and candles can
OL,9,Fbe lit in the Abbey in Holly's memory
OL,10,Fat any time during normal opening
OL,11,Fhours."
OL,13,FA 16-year-old boy, who cannot be named
OL,14,Ffor legal reasons, is accused of
OL,15,Fmurder, attempted murder and
OL,16,Fpossession of an offensive weapon.
OL,18,FThe courts are still deciding if the
OL,19,FGateshead teenager is fit to stand
OL,20,Ftrial.
